6 accordance with the Uniform Standards of Professional Appraisal
7 Practice.
8 H. The Tax Commission shall have the authority and duty to
9 prescribe forms and to promulgate rules as may be necessary to carry
10 out and administer the terms and provisions of this section.
11 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective January 1, 2027.
